Nigerian singer, Innocent Idibia, popularly Known as 2face went on his Twitter to hail the singing prowess of Simi. Simisola is currently pregnant for her husband and singer Adekunle Gold.
Tuface wrote in a tweet,
“I know say [COVID-19] wahala dey but why are we doing like @SympLySimi is not phenomenal,” he tweeted. Simi on the other hand replied with the most heartwarming tweet.
Simi replied,
“Hay God. Some compliments are bigger than others”.
Innocent Ujah Idibia (born in Jos, Plateau State, Nigeria), known by his stage name 2Baba, is a Nigerian singer,songwriter, record producer, entrepreneur, philanthropist, Humanitarian, and activist. Prior to July 2014, he went by the stage name 2face Idibia. He is one of the most decorated and successful Afro pop artists in Africa, and is also one of the most bankable performing music artistes in Africa. With over 2 decades in the industry, 2Baba remains influential in the Nigerian Entertainment space.